attributionInfo.brokerName: Michelle Larnard Real Estate Group LLC

description: Classic South Boston loft style condo located close to major high ways and Logan airport.  Original hardwood floors, solid timber posts and beams and high ceilings give a cozy home feel while the open concept layout allows for easy entertaining. Remodeled kitchen with ample cabinets, center island, quartz counter tops and stainless appliances. Updated bath with tiled shower. Large bedroom alcove has partial walls. Walk in closet, AC, in-unit laundry and one DEEDED parking space (#18) in a fenced in lot, top off the perks of this condo. Pet friendly, professional management company, elevator and common patio.  Less than 1 mile to dog park, Pleasure Bay and Castle Island.  Minutes to Seaport and Financial Districts.
